{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_excu_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_excu_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"送葬人","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"针对其在任务中表现出的异常，第五厅枢机与送葬人进行了一场谈话。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_excu_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["费德里科"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_bg_26_g12_laterano_office.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$tech_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_sys_tech_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","duration":"1.5","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"姓名，费德里科·吉亚洛。","id":11,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"是的。目前生理指标一切正常，没有不适情况。","id":13,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"随时可以接受问询。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"只是谈话，不是问询？明白，我会在我所知范围内如实回答所有提问。","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"请说。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":20},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"text","text":"这不是我第一次见到这个说话一板一眼的新人。","id":22},{"type":"text","text":"中庭公证所上一年招收了三名见习执行者，其中两名很遗憾最终未能加入我们。","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"其中一人没能通过实习期的考核，另一人忽然发现还是继承家里的甜品店更适合自己，于是在转正前一天递交辞呈。","id":24},{"type":"text","text":"最后剩下的，就是这名叫费德里科的年轻人。","id":25},{"type":"dialog","id":26},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":27},{"type":"dialog","id":28},{"type":"charslot","id":29},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"31","text":"费德里科，我希望可以再听你叙述一遍你的任务经过。"}},"values":[],"id":30},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":31,"end":39},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"明白。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"本次任务由中庭公证所派发，契约人为一位已故拉特兰公民。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"契约人在遗嘱中写明，希望公证所为他寻找失散在外的后人，并将其带回拉特兰。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"因遗嘱执行难度较高，本次委托由两名执行者共同完成。我已将遗嘱继承人带回，其身份已经确认。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":40},{"type":"charslot","id":41},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"43","text":"报告中提到，你的搭档在任务途中牺牲。"},"2":{"id":"48","text":"报告中提到，你本人在行动中受了重伤。"}},"values":[],"id":42},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":43,"end":47},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"是的。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"执行者贝托尼在行动过程中殉职。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":48,"end":52},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"记录无误。","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"冲击伤三处，穿刺伤一处，均不致命，已接受治疗。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png","end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2"],"id":53},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在本次任务执行期间，我与执行者贝托尼依据公民遗嘱，进入玻利瓦尔边境地带寻找其遗嘱继承人。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"该地区目前正处于战乱状态，缺乏稳定的社会秩序。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"遗嘱继承人被卷入当地武装冲突中，这对我们完成任务造成了一定阻碍。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在寻人途中，我们共遭遇三次混战，遗嘱继承人一度被挟持，执行者贝托尼因此身负重伤。","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"执行者贝托尼伤势很重，以当时的医疗条件很难进行有效救助。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"其本人对自己的情况做出了判断，并制定了下一步的行动方案。","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在他的计划里，他将成为诱饵吸引各方注意，而我在掩护下行动，确保遗嘱继承人的人身安全。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在当时的情况下，这确实是合理的安排。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":70},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":71},{"type":"text","text":"关于任务的叙述，到此为止没有半句谎言。","id":72},{"type":"text","text":"我们的执行者会被派往最危险的地带执行任务，因公殉职也并非个例。","id":73},{"type":"text","text":"但是费德里科的情况稍显特殊。","id":74},{"type":"text","text":"负责与其对接的同僚显然有些忧虑，因此我才站在这里，向这个年轻人问话。","id":75},{"type":"dialog","id":76},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"dialog","id":78},{"type":"charslot","id":79},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"81","text":"但是你并没有按照他的计划行动。"}},"values":[],"id":80},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":81,"end":91},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"恕我直言，执行者贝托尼的计划与我们需要执行的遗嘱有冲突之处。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"遗嘱中除明确要求公证所代为找回后人，将其护送回到拉特兰以外，还有其他申请条目。","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"“希望所有拉特兰人终归故土。”","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"这是他附加在遗嘱最后的申请。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"既然公证所已经受理其遗嘱，确保其全部内容得到执行就是我的工作。","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":92},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"text","text":"“希望所有拉特兰人终归故土。”","id":94},{"type":"text","text":"这是个多美好的期许。但我能说，它是需要被执行的遗嘱的一部分吗？","id":95},{"type":"text","text":"我看着面前这双眼。","id":96},{"type":"text","text":"它们坚硬，平静，没有丝毫涟漪。","id":97},{"type":"text","text":"我真希望我能够透过这片淡蓝色，看出一点什么来。","id":98},{"type":"dialog","id":99},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"执行者贝托尼的计划中，对其自身的规划并不明确。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"玻利瓦尔边境局势混乱，各方人员混杂，其中并不乏对拉特兰怀有敌意的势力。","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在这样的情况下，我无法听从安排，带遗嘱继承人先行离开。","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"请见谅。","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":109},{"type":"charslot","id":110},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"112","text":"你很清楚你将贝托尼背回拉特兰时，他是什么状态吧？"}},"values":[],"id":111},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":112,"end":122},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"是的。我很清楚。","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"执行者贝托尼在我们尝试脱围时，已经基本失去行动能力，因此之后的安排中由我背负其行动。","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"成年男子的体重尚在可承受的负重范围内，并没有太大问题。","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"当时他的失血量已超过人体可承受界限，体温下降到危险状态，其本人很快失去意识。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"脱离玻利瓦尔边境当天，执行者贝托尼确认死亡。","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":123},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"text","text":"这绝不是我第一次耳闻同僚的离去。也不会是最后一次。","id":125},{"type":"text","text":"我不禁思考，如果死者当真有知，贝托尼现在会怎么想？","id":126},{"type":"text","text":"他会愿意见到这个年轻人，为将自己带回拉特兰而身受重伤，甚至险些送命吗？","id":127},{"type":"dialog","id":128},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"dialog","id":130},{"type":"charslot","id":131},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"133","text":"贝托尼一定不同意你这么做。"}},"values":[],"id":132},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":133,"end":141},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"执行者贝托尼确实表示反对。","id":135,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"但他无法给其反对附加合理的解释，因此我选择维持我的判断。","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"结合任务与当时情况，契约人的遗嘱执行为当时的最高优先级，执行者贝托尼的个人意愿优先度较低。","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"如有特殊情况，我会列入考虑。","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":142},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":143},{"type":"text","text":"这就是我了解到的，关于费德里科·吉亚洛的另一特殊之处——","id":144},{"type":"text","text":"这个年轻人在共感能力上有所缺失。","id":145},{"type":"text","text":"在此之前我们的判断是，这种缺失并不会影响其作为执行者的工作。","id":146},{"type":"text","text":"只是现在看来，或许我需要重新对这一结论进行评判。","id":147},{"type":"dialog","id":148},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"dialog","id":150},{"type":"charslot","id":151},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"153","text":"费德里科，难道你认为贝托尼的意愿并不重要？"},"2":{"id":"156","text":"或许你要尝试站在贝托尼的角度来考虑他那时的心情。"}},"values":[],"id":152},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":153,"end":155},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我尊重执行者贝托尼的意愿。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":156,"end":158},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"恕我直言，我不明白这样做的意义。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png","end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2"],"id":159},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"执行者贝托尼是本次任务的参与成员之一，身为执行者，确保契约人的遗嘱顺利执行是我们共同的意愿。","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在这一点上我不认为存有异议。","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":164},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":165},{"type":"text","text":"我开始想要叹气了。","id":166},{"type":"text","text":"贝托尼最后想要以自己为诱饵，所图为何呢？","id":167},{"type":"text","text":"眼前的年轻人却反而冲入混战，差一点就要付出昂贵的代价，带着满身的伤痕也要将贝托尼带回......","id":168},{"type":"text","text":"他是否当真毫不在意？","id":169},{"type":"text","text":"他是否当真完全无法理解......贝托尼最后的那丁点期望？","id":170},{"type":"dialog","id":171},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"dialog","id":173},{"type":"charslot","id":174},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"176","text":"费德里科，你能明白我现在的情绪吗？"},"2":{"id":"188","text":"费德里科，你是否真的完全不懂情感？"}},"values":[],"id":175},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":176,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"text","text":"面前的年轻人没有说话。","id":179},{"type":"text","text":"他注视着我，像是在判断什么。但是判断什么呢？","id":180},{"type":"text","text":"忽然，他有了动作。","id":181},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科拿起一支笔，在桌面上的白纸上画下了什么。","id":182},{"type":"text","text":"他画了一个圆。","id":183},{"type":"dialog","id":184},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":185},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"您的情绪代表悲伤。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":188,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":189},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"text","text":"面前的年轻人没有说话。","id":191},{"type":"text","text":"他注视着我，像是在思考什么。","id":192},{"type":"text","text":"忽然，他有了动作。","id":193},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科拿起一支笔，在桌面上的白纸上画下了什么。","id":194},{"type":"text","text":"他画了一个方形。","id":195},{"type":"dialog","id":196},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":197},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"这场谈话中存有质疑。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png","end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2"],"id":200},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在刚才您对我的询问中，包含有试探、疑惑、悲伤以及其他多种情感。","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":203},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"text","text":"年轻的执行者在纸上画下了更多线条。","id":205},{"type":"dialog","id":206},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":207},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我不明白情感的成因，也难以理解情感对人的意义，但我能够理解这一结果。","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"不同的情感可以被线条替代，直线与曲线构成不同的图案，这对我很有帮助。","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"由于天生的生理缺陷，我无法如多数同胞一般与人共感。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"但这并不会对我在公证所的任职造成影响。","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我会完成交给我的委托。如有必要，我会去理解契约人的情感。","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":218},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":219},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科说到这里，忽然停顿了片刻。","id":220},{"type":"text","text":"我的心情此时已因为他的回答而大有改变，这个年轻人却说出了更加出乎所有人意料的话。","id":221},{"type":"dialog","id":222},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":223},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"关于执行者贝托尼殉职的后续处理，我已向公证所提交了遗嘱执行申请。","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在执行最终行动之前，贝托尼曾向我提及：","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"“如果这次能活着回去，我一定要参加大教堂前那家冰淇淋店的十球挑战。”","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"“要是运气差回不去，那就委托费德里科你帮我吃他个一百球吧！”","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"——以上即是执行者贝托尼的口述遗嘱。","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":234},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"text","text":"......这或许只是贝托尼的自嘲，或是一个玩笑。","id":236},{"type":"text","text":"我终于忍不住打断费德里科的话。","id":237},{"type":"text","text":"他画下的那些线条组成种种几何图形，有序地排列在纸上，看在我眼中却毫无规律可言。","id":238},{"type":"text","text":"我忍不住猜测，这其中是否有一个图形，正属于说出这些话语时的贝托尼？","id":239},{"type":"dialog","id":240},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":241},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"枢机阁下，我有能力判别信息的真实与否。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"尽管我无法与他共感，但我有类似的经验，能够判断说话者是否确有此意。","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"因接受错误的信号而导致误解的情况少有发生。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":248},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"text","text":"费德里科从始至终神色平静，任谁也会觉得这是个冰冷的、无情的人。","id":250},{"type":"text","text":"几分钟前，我尚在判断共感能力的缺失是否会对他在公证所的工作造成影响。","id":251},{"type":"text","text":"现在，我已开始为这个年轻人的表现叹息。","id":252},{"type":"text","text":"我问自己，费德里科·吉亚洛确实有所缺陷，但这又如何呢？","id":253},{"type":"text","text":"难道因为有缺陷，就能说他是一个不通情感，思维机械，无法感受的人吗？","id":254},{"type":"dialog","id":255},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":256},{"type":"dialog","id":257},{"type":"charslot","id":258},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"260","text":"这种通过线条解读情感的方式也是你天生就领悟的吗？"}},"values":[],"id":259},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":260,"end":264},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":262,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"不，是我的双亲教会我使用这种方法。","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":265},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":266},{"type":"text","text":"这个年轻人首次在问答中有了迟疑。","id":267},{"type":"text","text":"我看到他在说话的同时，手又动了起来，在那张白纸上画出了更多的图形。","id":268},{"type":"text","text":"但这一次我不必，也不应该开口询问其含义。","id":269},{"type":"dialog","id":270},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"他们曾是戍卫队特勤队成员，后转调公证所成为执行者，在执行任务过程中殉职。","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"令我能够理解情感是他们遗嘱的一部分，我目睹他们的死亡，并在那时首次尝试解读。","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"遗憾、不舍。","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"与执行者贝托尼的情况有类似的部分。","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"嗯？","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"您的情绪再次有所变化。为什么？","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":285},{"type":"text","text":"我无法回答这个问题。","id":286},{"type":"text","text":"我确信在经历多年的职业生涯之后，我已不会再轻易将情绪向外展露。","id":287},{"type":"text","text":"但这个年轻人却说得如此笃定，毫不怀疑。","id":288},{"type":"text","text":"身为中庭公证所的执行者，我们比其他拉特兰人要更容易见到人生百态，从生者到死者我们都要与之往来。","id":289},{"type":"text","text":"从这种意义上来说，费德里科或许才是我们之中，真正毫无杂念的那一个。","id":290},{"type":"text","text":"我想......他确实会是一名合格的送葬人。","id":291},{"type":"dialog","id":292},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"dialog","id":294},{"type":"charslot","id":295},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"297","text":"感谢你回答了我的所有疑问。"}},"values":[],"id":296},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":297,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":298},{"type":"charslot","id":299},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"301","text":"费德里科，接下来你有什么打算？"}},"values":[],"id":300},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":301,"end":307},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"虽然缺乏正式的申请手续，仅为当事人口述，但执行者贝托尼的遗嘱有另一名执行者为其见证。","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在这样的情况下，我认为可以将他的口述当作正式遗嘱看待。","id":305,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"因此，我会申请为其执行遗嘱。","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":308},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#2","id":309},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":310},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"text","text":"说到这里，年轻的执行者头一次神色微动。","id":312},{"type":"text","text":"他略微皱起眉。","id":313},{"type":"dialog","id":314},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":315},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#2","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......我已申请购买一百个冰淇淋球的执行经费。","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e9/Avg_char_279_excu_2.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"不论如何......","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_279_excu_4#1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我会完成生者与死者交予我的嘱托。","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c3/Avg_char_279_excu_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":322},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":323},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":324},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":325},{"type":"character","id":326},{"type":"image","id":327}],"characters":["费德里科"]}